<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Changed - Comic Reader</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #6d28d9; /* comic-purple */
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .alert {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">Comic Reader</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Your Password Has Been Changed</h2>
        
        <p>Hello{% if user.name %} {{ user.name }}{% endif %},</p>
        
        <p>We're writing to confirm that your password for your Comic Reader account was changed on {{ changeTime|date('F j, Y, g:i a') }}.</p>
        
        <div class="alert">
            <p><strong>If you made this change</strong>, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
            <p><strong>If you didn't make this change</strong>, please contact us immediately by replying to this email.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>For security reasons, we recommend:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Using unique passwords for each of your online accounts</li>
            <li>Never sharing your password with anyone</li>
            <li>Changing your password periodically</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent to {{ user.email }} to notify you about important changes to your account.</p>
        <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Comic Reader. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
